data.description: This (almost 1/2 acre) lakefront  CBS 3/2 with a 1 car garage has: a new roof, impact windows, a/c (2021), newer water heater, new garage door and opener. The open floorplan leads to a large family/Florida room with it's own mini-split a/c overlooking the lake. The home is fully handicap accessible.  Maybe a gas whole house generator (22kw) is what you are looking for. Check that box off. Incredible opportunity in Florida Gardens and on a lake!!!!
